  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); height: 300px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
    <div>
      <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🥕</div>
      <div>AI IMAGE: Vegetable Consommé</div>
      <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-weight: normal;">Crystal-clear vegetable broth in elegant bowl, light golden color</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div style="padding: 2.5rem;">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); color: white; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600;">Recipe #2</div>
      <div style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.9rem;">🌱 Vegan • Low Sodium</div>
    </div>
    
    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #1f2937; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800;">Vegetable Consommé</h3>
    
    <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      A crystal-clear, flavorful broth made from fresh vegetables. Perfect for vegans/vegetarians and anyone who prefers plant-based options during their first post-surgery week.
    </p>
    
